data.description: Experience luxury and versatility in this 5-bed, 4-full-bath, 2-half-bath townhouse in Davenport. Granite countertops, tile flooring downstairs, and wood laminate upstairs offer style and comfort. Short-term rentals are allowed, making it an ideal investment or primary residence. Enjoy the screened-in pool, clubhouse, pool, water play area, and fitness center. Minutes from theme parks, this property is your Florida haven – seize the opportunity today!
